	"keywords": "Community, Open Source",
	"description": "I&#x27;ve been sending my &quot;5 freeCodeCamp resources worth your time&quot; for 8 years now.\nThat&#x27;s nearly 400 emails that I&#x27;ve authored and sent out over the years.\n\nDon&#x27;t worry. I&#x27;m not tired. I love doing this, I&#x27;m going to keep working hard to\nshare helpful learning resources with you.\n\nI just need to make sure you&#x27;re actually reading these emails. Please fill out\nthis Google form real quick. It will take less than 1 minute.\n[https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfwh2v6SoldZiFOE8yE_r7OqbJmBjH6i2Z9Pi",
	"headline": "Quincy&#x27;s 5 freeCodeCamp Resources Worth Your Time Email – You Need to Re-subscribe Real Quick",
