	"keywords": "Gamedev, Podcast, YouTube",
	"description": "On this week&#x27;s episode of the podcast, I interview Jabril. He&#x27;s an indie game\ndeveloper who&#x27;s building a turn-based fighting game called Ultrabouters.\n\nJabril has developed tons of other games as well. He runs the popular Jabrils\ngamedev focused-YouTube. He&#x27;s also published a 5-hour introduction to\nprogramming course on freeCodeCamp.\n\nWe talk about:\n\n * How Jabril got into gamedev as a kid when he got a copy of GameMaker\n * Jabril&#x27;s career working at a comedy club and a radio station\n * The anim",
	"headline": "Indie Game Dev Jabrils talks AI, Anime, and How to Build Games [freeCodeCamp Podcast #118]",
